commentary: Rohan Mustafa to Berrington, FOUR runs swept to long leg boundary for four runs, and that's Berrington's 50 ODI and he scores the winning runs! Scotland win with 2.2 overs to spare, thanks to that epic 165 run 3rd wicket partnership
